snippet.title: Cynthiam106
snippet.description: Hello Friends, My name is Cynthia and I am currently a stay at home mom of 3 boys. My boys are my life and they are 13, 9, and 6 years old. I am also a dog mom of a 1 year old maltipoo who I also love with all my heart. On my channel you will find a lot of haul videos especially when it comes to makeup, bath and body works, TJ Maxx, Target, etc.. I love get ready with me videos and favorites videos as well. I would say that this is more of a lifestyle channel so subscribe and get to know me a little more.
